<p> 
<seg id=2> The New China News Agency Hangzhou on September first news (Reporter Zhu Guo Xian, trainee managed wise sunshine) since childhood becomes the orphan and is bold in Hangzhou child welfare Chair big deformed student Ding, other day received the Hangzhou University's admission notice, became this school philosophy and the social sciences department's student. </seg>
<seg id=3> It is reported, this year 19 year old Ding Hao is new Chinese first the deformed orphan university student which grows by the welfare courtyard adoption. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=4> " Receives the written notice, I really want to jump ", Ding Hao said, but he actually are unable to use " to jump " express oneself the excited sentiment. </seg>
<seg id=5> When three years old one high fever, caused him to suffer from the serious small paralysis sequela, this one year he by welfare courtyard adoption. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=6> Ding Hao reads the elementary school in the child welfare courtyard, afterwards enters neighbor on the native place one school the junior middle school. </seg>
<seg id=7> As soon as starts by welfare courtyard teacher to send and pick up, after the second day lives at school, each Saturday returns to the welfare courtyard, regardless of blows the wind rains, ever is not absent from class. </seg>
<seg id=8> This year, he enroll the college entrance examination, and enrolls by the qualified result by the Hangzhou University. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=9> The Ding Hao success, condensed the social from all walks of life painstaking care. </seg>
<seg id=10> The child welfare courtyard 16 years like one day the care, cherishes him, since last year, only has been he pays the school expense, buys the material, buys the nutriment, spend more than 3000 Yuan Renminbi. </seg>
<seg id=11> The society from all walks of life also stretched out hand the aid to him. </seg>
<seg id=12> After knows Ding boldly tests attend university, the Hangzhou Longchang cooking oil trading company donates money 20000 Yuan, subsidized on him the university, unit and so on artificial limb factory delivers the wheelchair, the walking stick to him and so on. </seg>
</p> 
